<h1 class="entry-title c-heading-3">Microsoft Inspire: Accelerating AI transformation through partnership</h1>
<div>
<p class="c-meta-text"><time datetime="2023-07-18"><abbr title="July 18, 2023">Jul 18, 2023</abbr>&nbsp;</time><span class="c-meta-divider-space">|</span>&nbsp;<a class="c-hyperlink u-underline" title="Frank X. Shaw" href="https://blogs.microsoft.com/blog/author/frankxshaw/" aria-label="See more written by Frank X. Shaw">Frank X. Shaw - Chief Communications Officer, Microsoft</a></p>
</div>
<div class="c-social f-horizontal">
<div class="mt-social-links">
<ul class="mt-social-links__list horizontal">
<li class="mt-social-links__item"><a class="mt-social-links__link" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.microsoft.com%2Fblog%2F2023%2F07%2F18%2Fmicrosoft-inspire-accelerating-ai-transformation-through-partnership%2F&amp;t=Microsoft+Inspire%3A+Accelerating+AI+transformation+through+partnership" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="mt-social-links__text"><span class="screen-reader-text">Share on Facebook (opens new window)</span></span></a></li>
<li class="mt-social-links__item"><a class="mt-social-links__link" href="https://twitter.com/share?text=Microsoft+Inspire%3A+Accelerating+AI+transformation+through+partnership&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.microsoft.com%2Fblog%2F2023%2F07%2F18%2Fmicrosoft-inspire-accelerating-ai-transformation-through-partnership%2F" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="mt-social-links__text"><span class="screen-reader-text">Share on Twitter (opens new window)</span></span></a></li>
